data.description: This home has it all. Newer carpet throughout the house with central vacuum. Awesome theater room for entertaining with projector and 120" powered screen in oversized family room, with "RBH" in wall surround sound speakers. Large, covered patio. Brand new roof in Fall of 2022. Fully fenced yard with infrared security cameras in quiet neighborhood. Recently renovated master bath. Two newer High Efficiency furnaces that also include U.V. air purifiers. LOTS of storage inside. Tower for "HAM" radio and a generator for the house that runs on propane also included.
